abstract: Temple Emanu-El was the setting yesterday for the marriage of Miss Aileen Hendricks Lewisohn, daughter of Mrs. Frankenthaler Lewisohn and Richard Lewisohn of New York, to Dr. Peter Alan Godsick, son of Dr. and Mrs. William Howard Godsick of New York and Elberon, N.J.

abstract: The premiere of a new production of "Romeo et Juliette" at the Metropolitan Opera House on Sept. 19 will benefit the Production Fund of the Metropolitan Opera Association. The Met's season opens Sept. 18 with last year's production of "La Traviata."
